<div id="gs-site-change-name">
  <h2>Change the Site Name</h2>
  <p>
    The site name is shown at the top of every page on the site, in
    the body of many page, and in email messages sent from this site.
    To change the site name, carry out the following tasks.
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to the <cite>Change Name</cite> page.</li>
    <li>Enter the name for the site in the
      <samp class="entry">Name</samp> entry.
    </li>
    <li>Click the <samp class="button">Change</samp> button.
      The name of the site will be updated.
    </li>
  </ol>
</div><!--gs-site-change-name-->
